{"tid":1118444,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"［真心話］作為喜愛動漫嘅偽娘\\LGBT 希望大家可以多啲包容 少啲歧視","createTime":"2019-04-21T12:09:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T02:14:24.000Z","uid":146340,"like":35,"dislike":58,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"79508133da992223adf2e92be21348d3559f8b71","tid":1118444,"uid":146340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T12:09:07.000Z","msg":"其實香港動漫界/cos界歧視性小眾嘅風氣一直都好犀利 其他地方好似內地、台灣甚至韓國、日本都好包容 好接受 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">就係香港充滿住偏見同歧視</span><br />\n<br />\n依幅係我未咁識化妝嘅時候影嘅相<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PLnCGO1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPLnCGO1.png&h=92fc1c1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係依段時候好多人鼓勵我，幫過禾 不過都有好多人笑我 話我似男人 話我樣衰 講好多難聽嘅說話 <br />\n<br />\ncos圈同社會都好似連登依個論壇甘 好多負能量 淨係識批評 但係我靠住朋友既鼓勵都一一撐過來！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係我識得選擇唔聽haters嘅說話 唔係我明白做人最緊要正面嘅面對haters，我都唔會有勇氣變靚自己 而家嘅我就同以前已經好唔同<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bHYa1Q0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbHYa1Q0.png&h=f54373af&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KeZ5QKm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKeZ5QKm.png&h=fbf08962&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後我想同haters講：你地嘅批評只係證明你地充滿偏見同埋不快樂<br />\n<br />\n想同同我一樣嘅性小眾講：加油！唔好比haters控制你地嘅life！要堅強！"},{"pid":"8c36b6bef3ab73a4a04093390630566d214690a4","tid":1118444,"uid":21456,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T12:15:06.000Z","msg":"我醉愛直葉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c661a227e96c9e72f117246bdf156fa4bf27a17","tid":1118444,"uid":3020,"like":7,"dislike":15,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T12:15:57.000Z","msg":"女扮男<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wCpQ1UL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwCpQ1UL.png&h=fb7ae1ab&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EJEdZGq.pn